# MCP Server Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your actual values
# Then set these as system environment variables (see MCP_SETUP.md for instructions)

# GitHub Personal Access Token
# Required for: GitHub MCP Server
# Get it from: https://github.com/settings/tokens
# Scopes needed: repo, workflow, read:user
GITHUB_TOKEN=your_github_token_here

# Brave Search API Key
# Required for: Brave Search MCP Server
# Get it from: https://brave.com/search/api/
BRAVE_API_KEY=your_brave_api_key_here

# Note: These environment variables should be set at the system level, not just in .env
# See MCP_SETUP.md for platform-specific instructions on setting environment variables
